[p 
	"About v4, many people complained of the usage of the pause trick as
	$LF
	"a "cheap" way to kill enemies. Therefore I used it as little as
	$LF
	"possible now. It was only used as a last resort when otherwise
	$LF
	"there would be loss of time. In fact, avoiding the trick sometimes
	$LF
	[em 
		"gained
	]em
	" speed in the form of lag reduction.
	$LF
]p
[p 
	"Ps: I'm sure that some people would like to know.
	$LF
	"Besides the fact that this movie was played 
	[em 
		[a href=/Glossary 
			"tool-assisted
		]a
	]em
